isy, kt\u00f3re przyci\u0105gn\u0105 uwag\u0119 widza.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Nowy format reklam wideo to znakomity spos\u00f3b na opowiedzenie historii o Twoim produkcie i przyci\u0105gni\u0119cie klient\u00f3w, zw\u0142aszcza w okresie przed\u015bwi\u0105tecznym, kiedy konkurencja jest najwi\u0119ksza. Zach\u0119camy do eksperymentowania z tym formatem, monitorowania wynik\u00f3w oraz dostosowywania strategii w miar\u0119 potrzeb.<\/p>\n<p>Podsumowuj\u0105c, wideo mo\u017ce by\u0107 pot\u0119\u017cnym narz\u0119dziem w Twojej kampanii reklamowej. Przeanalizuj swoje dzia\u0142ania i b\u0105d\u017a otwarty na zmiany.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h2>Jak skutecznie wykorzysta\u0107 nowy format reklam wideo na Amazonie?<\/h2>\n<p>Czy wiesz, \u017ce Amazon wpro<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":5124,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[5],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-5123","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-strategia"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5123"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=5123"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5123\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/5124"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=5123"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href